data.description: **This property is located in a geographic area that is eligible for a $10,000 grant offered via Prosperity Home Mortgage.  There is no income requirements to receive the grant but it must be an owner occupied property to qualify.**  INCOME-GENERATING DUPLEX steps from hospitals, universities, transportation hubs, and wonderful restaurants! Experience modern living in this exceptional University City Income Producing duplex, boasting a brand new roof installed in 2021 and impeccable upkeep, ensuring it stands in pristine condition. Nestled just steps away from UPENN, CHOP, VA Hospital, and University of the Sciences, this gem offers an array of enticing features. This bright and ultra-modern duplex is ideally located in the highly sought-after University City area and is situated within the prestigious Penn Alexander School District. This property is also a great opportunity for a buyer looking to reside in the primary unit with access to the private backyard and driveway, which can accommodate up to two to three vehicles, while supplementing their mortgage with rental income. As you walk up to this duplex, you will appreciate the artful exterior design and meticulously maintained grounds that include a tiered side yard adorned with beautiful plantings. Adding to the allure is a captivating mosaic mural that spans the driveway, created by the renowned artist Isaiah Zagar, whose celebrated work adorns over 100 public walls throughout the city, including Philadelphia's famous Magic Gardens. Step inside, and you'll find a wealth of appealing details, including hardwood floors and sleek and modern kitchens. The primary unit features an open layout kitchen, with stainless steel cabinets and a spacious island. Hardwood flooring graces the upper levels, enhancing the overall aesthetic. Washer & Dryer included in the common area and can be converted to coin op for additional income. The property is a block away from the trolley portal where trolley lines 11, 13, 34, 36, can be easily accessed, making it a breeze to connect to the Broad Street and Market-Frankford Lines and 30th Street Station. Don't pass up the chance to own this remarkable property in the best location. This is a great opportunity for a buyer looking to be in an income generating, owner-occupied property, or an investor looking for an easily rentable property in a central location. RENTALS ARE PROJECTED BASED ON IF THE ENTIRE BUILDING WAS FULLY RENTED.
